_sText:
UPDATE! The map now has 6 working spawn points a side, working rain, ladders and a whole bunch of other stuff. Check out the screenshots or download it and play it. Don't forget to rate and comment :D

Well, here it is. My first map. I decided to make a small gungame map, because its simple and easy to make. 3 spawn points for each team, a buyzone for each team and a working skybox. I was going to make a room under it but i haven't figured out how to make working ladders yet. Enjoy!
